>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=You+Are+Not+So+Smart&amp;rft.atitle=The+Illusion+of+Transparency&amp;rft.date=2010-07-14&amp;rft.aulast=McRaney&amp;rft.aufirst=David&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fyouarenotsosmart.com%2F2010%2F07%2F14%2Fthe-illusion-of-transparency%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AIllusion+of+transparency\" class=\"Z3988\"></span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291\"/></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite id=\"CITEREFIreland2016\" class=\"citation book cs1\">Ireland, Christopher (2016). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://eprints.hud.ac.uk/id/eprint/27264/1/Paper%201317%20INTED%202016%20by%20Ireland.pdf\">\"Student Oral Presentations: Developing the Skills and Reducing the Apprehension\"</a> <span class=\"cs1-format\">(PDF)</span>. <i>INTED2016 Proceedings</i>. <b>1</b>. pp.&#160;1474\u20131483. <a href=\"/wiki/Doi_(identifier)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Doi (identifier)\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.21125%2Finted.2016.1317\">10.21125/inted.2016.1317</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"ISBN (identifier)\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-84-608-5617-7\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-84-608-5617-7\"><bdi>978-84-608-5617-7</bdi></a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=Student+Oral+Presentations%3A+Developing+the+Skills+and+Reducing+the+Apprehension&amp;rft.btitle=INTED2016+Proceedings&amp;rft.pages=1474-1483&amp;rft.date=2016&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.21125%2Finted.2016.1317&amp;rft.isbn=978-84-608-5617-7&amp;rft.aulast=Ireland&amp;rft.aufirst=Christopher&am